Package: influxr
Title: Query InfluxDB v2 with Flexible Time Handling and Caching
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Tom", "Parkinson", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "tom@example.com")
Description: Retrieve data from InfluxDB v2 buckets using Flux queries via
    httr2. Handles timezone conversion, monthly query chunking, compressed
    file caching, and incremental dataset updates.
